{"text_id":103202,"tokens":["The"," debate"," on"," whether"," students"," should"," be"," required"," to"," have"," a"," B"," in"," Physical"," Education"," (","P",".","E",".)"," in"," order"," to"," participate"," in"," physical"," activities"," at"," school"," is"," a"," contentious"," one","."," While"," it"," is"," understandable"," that"," schools"," may"," want"," to"," incentiv","ize"," academic"," achievement",","," implementing"," a"," GPA"," requirement"," for"," extracurricular"," activities"," could"," have"," unintended"," consequences","."," Ex","cluding"," students"," who"," do"," not"," meet"," this"," requirement"," could"," potentially"," impact"," their"," physical"," health",","," academic"," performance",","," and"," overall"," well","-","being",".","\n\n","First",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," recognize"," the"," role"," of"," P",".","E","."," in"," promoting"," healthy"," habits","."," P",".","E","."," classes"," offer"," students"," the"," opportunity"," to"," engage"," in"," regular"," physical"," activity",","," develop"," motor"," skills",","," and"," learn"," about"," the"," importance"," of"," maintaining"," a"," healthy"," lifestyle","."," By"," excluding"," students"," who"," do"," not"," meet"," a"," certain"," GPA"," requirement",","," schools"," are"," denying"," them"," the"," opportunity"," to"," develop"," these"," essential"," skills"," and"," habits","."," Moreover",","," research"," has"," shown"," that"," regular"," physical"," activity"," can"," improve"," academic"," performance",","," reduce"," stress"," and"," anxiety",","," and"," promote"," overall"," well","-","being","."," Therefore",","," denying"," students"," access"," to"," physical"," activity"," could"," have"," the"," opposite"," effect"," of"," what"," schools"," intend",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," implementing"," a"," GPA"," requirement"," for"," physical"," activities"," could"," disproportion","ately"," affect"," students"," from"," low","-","inco